Statement of Purpose

The laws of most jurisdictions throughout the world automatically confer
exclusive Copyright and Related Rights (defined below) upon the creator and
subsequent owner(s) (each and all, referred to in this document as the "owner")
of the original work of authorship and/or any database.

Certain persons, however, may have an interest in the work and would like to
cooperate with the creator to ensure that the work is freely available for
everyone to build upon.

This document explicitly releases that work to the public domain.

